data.description: Contemporary beauty sitting on .34 acres in established Durham neighborhood! Updated kitchen ft. granite counters, SS appliances, modern cabinets/hardware, & tile backsplash. Refinished hardwoods and fresh paint throughout! Upgraded baths w/ custom tile work. Lower level ft. expansive family room w/ wood burning fireplace & custom built-ins. Outdoor features incl. perfectly situated lot ft. large patio w/ built-in grill overlooking fenced in backyard, multiple sheds/detached garage, and oversized carport. Minutes away from Downtown Durham, Duke University, & easy access to 15-501 & 40/540. Interactive 3D Virtual Tour & Aerial Video Available! No HOA. Roof (2021). HVAC (2012).
